Serie

public Serie(java.util.List<T> data)
A serie contains data, stored as a List. This data can be : a Number, a Point @see Point, a Bubble @see Bubble or a PiePiece @see PiePiece, depending on the chart type

Parameters:
data - : the data to plot on the chart
